- content_for :title, "Privacy Policy"
- content_for :description, "Bookify privacy policy. How we handle your data."

.row.justify-content-center.mt-4
  .col-md-8
    %h1.fw-bold Privacy Policy
    %p.text-muted Last updated: 30 March 2026

    .card.border-0.shadow-sm.my-4
      .card-body.p-4
        %h4.fw-bold Who we are
        %p
          Bookify is operated by
          %strong Skiwo AS
          (org. 916 636 660), Pilestredet 17, 0164 Oslo, Norway.
          Skiwo AS is the data controller for personal data processed through Bookify.
        %p.mb-0
          Contact:
          %a{href: "mailto:privacy@payoutpartner.com"} privacy@payoutpartner.com

    .card.border-0.shadow-sm.my-4
      .card-body.p-4
        %h4.fw-bold What we collect
        %p We collect the minimum data needed to operate Bookify:
        %ul
          %li
            %strong Email address
            — used for passwordless sign-in (magic link) and to identify your account.
          %li
            %strong Booking and payout data
            — descriptions, rates, and hours you enter when creating bookings.
          %li
            %strong PayoutPartner API credentials
            — if you enter sandbox API keys in Settings, they are stored to connect your account to PayoutPartner.
        %p.mb-0 We do not collect analytics, tracking cookies, or any data beyond what you explicitly provide.

    .card.border-0.shadow-sm.my-4
      .card-body.p-4
        %h4.fw-bold How we use your data
        %ul.mb-0
          %li To authenticate you via magic link email
          %li To display your bookings, freelancers, and payouts
          %li To communicate with the PayoutPartner API on your behalf
          %li We do not sell, share, or transfer your data to third parties other than PayoutPartner (as required to process payouts)

    .card.border-0.shadow-sm.my-4
      .card-body.p-4
        %h4.fw-bold Cookies
        %p.mb-0
          Bookify uses a single session cookie (
          %code _bookify_app_session
          ) to keep you signed in. This is a functional cookie required for the app to work.
          We do not use tracking cookies, analytics cookies, or any third-party cookies.

    .card.border-0.shadow-sm.my-4
      .card-body.p-4
        %h4.fw-bold Data storage and security
        %p.mb-0
          Data is stored in a PostgreSQL database hosted on Heroku (AWS EU region).
          All connections use TLS encryption. Access is restricted to authorised personnel only.

    .card.border-0.shadow-sm.my-4
      .card-body.p-4
        %h4.fw-bold Your rights
        %p Under GDPR, you have the right to:
        %ul
          %li Access the personal data we hold about you
          %li Request correction or deletion of your data
          %li Object to or restrict processing of your data
          %li Data portability
        %p.mb-0
          To exercise any of these rights, email
          %a{href: "mailto:privacy@payoutpartner.com"} privacy@payoutpartner.com
